schemaList.FormattedServiceName: Notify Business Travel Card Application Response
schemaList.FormattedDisplayName: Notify Business Travel Card Application Response (V1.0)

description:
Service Usage

This service is used to lodge an APEC BusinessTravel Card application, and also to update an applicants passport which is associated with the travel card.
readme:
Service Usage

This service is used to lodge an APEC BusinessTravel Card application, and also to update an applicants passport which is associated with the travel card.

Service Behaviour

PriorityEconomyICAOCode is 1 to many, but only up to five economies can be selected.

Transformation

The ESB transforms the NotifyBusinessTravelCardApplicationRequest.xsd message differently, depending on the request payload.

If the request is for an application creation (NotifyABTCCreate element exists), the message is transformed into a CreateApplicationExtendedRequest.xsd ABTC provider message.

If the request is for a passport update (NotifyABTCUpdatePassport element exists), the message is transformed into a UpdatePassportRequest.xsd ABTC provider message.
